                                        <h2>College Of Science and Mathematics</h2>
                                        <p>The College of Science and Mathematics envisions a world where scientific inquiry and mathematical reasoning are driving forces behind innovation, discovery, and sustainable progress. We aim to be a premier institution in science and mathematics education, research, and application, dedicated to producing highly skilled scientists, mathematicians, and researchers who excel in their fields and contribute significantly to the advancement of knowledge and technology. Our vision is to inspire a new generation of scholars and innovators who engage in cutting-edge research, foster interdisciplinary collaboration, and address complex global challenges through scientific and mathematical solutions.</p>
                                        <p>Our mission at the College of Science and Mathematics is to provide rigorous education, research, and training programs that prepare students for successful careers in scientific research, mathematics, technology, and related fields. We are committed to fostering a deep understanding of scientific principles, mathematical concepts, and analytical problem-solving skills. Through comprehensive academic curricula, laboratory experiences, and research opportunities, we empower our students to explore the frontiers of science and mathematics, conduct innovative research, and apply their knowledge to real-world problems.</p>
